HEADWORD: Pernancy
<hw>Per"nan*cy</hw> <pr>(p⟦etil⟧r"n⟦ait⟧n*s⟦ycr⟧)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<ety>[OF. <ets>prenance</ets>, fr. <ets>prendre</ets>,
<ets>prenre</ets>, <ets>penre</ets>, to take, L. <ets>prendere</ets>,
<ets>prehendere</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Law)</fld> <def>A taking or
